Home Embedded Dashboard

The Home embedded dashboard includes pipeline metrics, call reports (including any interactions between internal or external deal parties), and account insights.

Use the Dashboard

Use the Home Embedded dashboard for a comprehensive view of your deals, activities, and accounts.

KPI Calculations - Open Deals
Open Deals: Sum of Transaction Value from Financial Deal object where Deal status is in ["On Hold", "Open"].
Open Deals Over time: Sum of Transaction Value from Financial Deal object where Deal status is "Open" over time(Snapshot Date) for Current Year until Current Day.

KPI Calculations - Deals in Progress
Deals in progress: Count of Deals from Financial Deal Object where status is in ["On Hold", "Open"].
Deals in progress over time: Sum of TransactionValue from Financial Deal Object where status is in ["On Hold", "Open"] over time (Snapshot Date) for YTD.

KPI Calculations - Call Reports
Call Reports: Count of call reports(Interaction Summary object) created in YTD.
Call reports over time: Count of call reports created in YTD over CreatedDate.

KPI Calculations - Received Fee
Received Fee: Sum of ReceivedFee from Financial Deal object for YTD.
Received Fee over time: Sum of ReceivedFee from Financial Deal object where Deal status is "Open" over time(Snapshot Date) for Current Year until Current Day.
title: Understanding the Home Embedded Dashboard in Salesforce CRM Analytics
